The paper deals with the modeling and analysis of the effects of blockage in millimeter-wave cellular scenarios, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of the proposed model for system-level characterization and optimization, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), and systems and control (cs.SY).
